{"tid":1672731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個動作令國際社會明白加泰集會係聚焦反濫暴","createTime":"2019-10-24T09:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T11:46:11.000Z","uid":175954,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fe82e847fbdb511339b5cc093178fd6bdcb49ff9","tid":1672731,"uid":175954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:28:37.000Z","msg":"標題可能太誇張<br />\n但係我有個小建議<br />\n今晚去唔去加泰集會就自己決定<br />\n而決定要去嘅人就可以諗下做d嘢<br />\n去突顯呢場集會嘅主題<br />\n今晚去集會嘅人可以帶眼罩或者用紗布遮住其中一隻眼<br />\n因為我哋兩邊都有人比狂暴警爆眼<br />\n呢個舉動係代表香港加泰兩地都遭受到政府濫暴打壓<br />\n而今日出嚟集會嘅香港人就係因為親身體驗過/緊呢種暴力打壓 身同感受<br />\n所以先會有咁大迴響 行出嚟聲援加泰人<br />\n<br />\n順便附送兩條link<br />\n第一條係加泰警暴片<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2847975528559873&amp;id=117692491588204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2847975528559873%26id%3D117692491588204&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=74bd169a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2847975528559873&amp;id=117692491588204</a><br />\n<br />\n第二條係關注加泰記者同示威者遭受濫暴嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coe.int/en/web/commissioner/-/protection-of-the-rights-to-freedom-of-expression-and-peaceful-assembly-during-last-week-s-demonstrations-in-catalonia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coe.int%2Fen%2Fweb%2Fcommissioner%2F-%2Fprotection-of-the-rights-to-freedom-of-expression-and-peaceful-assembly-during-last-week-s-demonstrations-in-catalonia&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=a278b830\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coe.int/en/web/commissioner/-/protection-of-the-rights-to-freedom-of-expression-and-peaceful-assembly-during-last-week-s-demonstrations-in-catalonia</a>"},{"pid":"a11d2c9f9f86fefe1165571e413b3c532b52b388","tid":1672731,"uid":175954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d1d4fef2495ecea11960db670e02291eadeb6668","tid":1672731,"uid":